'''Sarah Corvo''' is an inhabitant of [[Port Phasmatys]] and descendant of the hero [[Tristan]], she is met during the [[Dragon Slayer II]] [[quest]]. She gives information on the location of the [[Morytania]] [[dragon key piece]], which she buried in the swamps to avoid letting the [[vampyre]]s get it. She was relieved to get rid of the key piece, believing it to be best if it was lost and forgotten.

